/**
 * There are lots of action type name const value
 */
export const AUTH_SUCCESS = 'auth_success' // login/register success
export const ERROR_MSG = 'error_msg' // error info
export const RECEIVE_USER = 'receive_user' // receive user
export const RESET_USER = 'reset_user' // reset user
export const RECEIVE_USER_LIST = 'receive_user_list' // receive user list data
export const RECEIVE_MSG_LIST = 'receive_msg_list' // receive msg list (all msg)
export const RECEIVE_MSG = 'receive_msg' // receive one msg
export const MSG_READ = 'msg_read' // msg read
